{"tid":1449374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:18:17.000Z","uid":163394,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"455df2df5deef1c795b1758702b987c91bbece86","tid":1449374,"uid":163394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:53:32.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcphR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=93ac5ec7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcphR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=4897b38a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"e0889006fe3c29921e565cc1b998876b87ebd4f6","tid":1449374,"uid":14433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:54:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"109771b7c7dea3564a0a58473553b0c85667f2a6","tid":1449374,"uid":14433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:54:12.000Z","msg":"812 下午一點機場接機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1449141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1449141</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"45130561b6a529614624795fa7f75709c85f85aa","tid":1449374,"uid":276911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:54:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4f1df2500d915f5697e8a233f14551